Enhancement: `restic repair snapshots --remove-ids` remoives broken snapshots

In the past restic had no command to remove broken snapshot files.

`restic repair snapshots --remove-ids` can now remove broken snapshot files,
which have been found previously by `restic check` or
by earlier error messages from restic.

`restic repair snapshots --remove-ids 1d204771` will remove a broken snapshot
file if such a snapshot exists. Otherwise an error will be raised.

https://github.com/restic/restic/issues/21892
https://github.com/restic/restic/pull/21907
